text: Opening your eyes, you come to realize you no longer reside on the plane of complacency. You now breathe, see, and walk on the plane of theodom. You have this feeling deep down in your gut that assures the world of your godliness. Turning around, you see a monumentous crowd of Ccaizhdi peoples, jaws bellowing and weapons thumping against shields. You utter your name - Ccaizhdi-zai! You win.
